ong",null,{"className":"font-bold text-white/90","children":"Watches the chain."}]," recv's watchers observe incoming transfers to your destination addresses and match them to open invoices."]}],"\n",["$","li",null,{"className":"text-base md:text-[1.0625rem] leading-[1.7] text-white/60 relative pl-6 [&>ul]:mt-3 [&_strong]:text-white/90 before:content-[''] before:absolute before:left-0 before:top-[0.7em] before:w-1.5 before:h-1.5 before:rounded-full before:bg-accent/50","children":[["$","strong",null,{"className":"font-bold text-white/90","children":"Confirms and notifies."}]," When a matching transfer is seen, the invoice transitions (",["$","code",null,{"className":"px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-md bg-white/[0.06] border border-white/10 text-accent text-[0.875em] font-mono whitespace-nowrap","children":"paid"}],", ",["$","code",null,{"className":"px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-md bg-white/[0.06] border border-white/10 text-accent text-[0.875em] font-mono whitespace-nowrap","children":"underpaid"}],", ",["$","code",null,{"className":"px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-md bg-white/[0.06] border border-white/10 text-accent text-[0.875em] font-mono whitespace-nowrap","children":"overpaid"}],", ",["$","code",null,{"className":"px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded-md bg-white/[0.06] border border-white/10 text-accent text-[0.875em] font-mono whitespace-nowrap","children":"manual_review"}],"), and recv fires a signed webhook to your endpoint."]}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","pre",null,{"className":"rounded-2xl bg-[#0a0a0c] border border-white/10 p-5 md:p-6 overflow-x-auto my-8 text-white/80 [&>code]:bg-transparent [&>code]:border-0 [&>code]:p-0 [&>code]:text-white/80","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"language-text","children":" Customer            recv                         You\n    │   pays on-chain   │                            │\n    │ ─────────────────►│  destination = YOUR wallet │\n    │                   │  (funds never touch recv) │\n    │                   │  matches transfer→invoice  │\n    │            